  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Change From Baseline in Daily Pain Score at Week 2</measure>
    <time_frame>Baseline, Week 2</time_frame>
    <description>Change from baseline in the daily-average-pain score at week 2. This was measured using a 11-point (0 to 10) scale where 0 represented no pain and 10 represented worst pain. Due to the low number of patients completing the treatment period of the study no analyses were performed</description>
  </primary_outcome>
